 formulated with gentle ingredients. The 2025 nut-free version also suits those with allergies.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-header\">Is Beard Butter vegan?<\/button>\n        <div class=\"accordion-content\">\n            <p>No, it contains beeswax. However, it is cruelty-free.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-header\">Is the packaging recyclable?<\/button>\n        <div class=\"accordion-content\">\n            <p>Yes, the matte black plastic jar is recyclable. Please clean it before recycling.<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-header\">What makes Beard Butter special?<\/button>\n        <div class=\"accordion-content\">\n            <p>\n                • Luxurious Hydration: Richer alternative to Beard Oil.<br>\n                • Travel-Friendly: Compact 50ml jar.<br>\n                • Perfect for Dry Beards: Targets dryness for a polished, healthy look.\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n    <p style=\"margin-top:20px;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/beardandbones.co.uk\/pages\/faq-2\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#1E90FF;\">Learn more<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n<style>\n.beard-butter-faq-container {\n    background: #111;\n    color: #fff;\n    padding: 20px;\n    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    max-width: 600px;\n    margin: 20px auto;\n}\n.beard-butter-faq-container h2 {\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n    text-align: center;\n}\n.beard-butter-faq-container .accordion-item {\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n}\n.beard-butter-faq-container .accordion-header {\n    width: 100%;\n    background: #222;\n    color: #fff;\n    padding: 10px;\n    text-align: left;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    border: none;\n    border-radius: 5px;\n    font-size: 16px;\n}\n.beard-butter-faq-container .accordion-content {\n    display: none;\n 